!SimpleFileBrowser methodsFor:'actions'!

fileDoubleClick
    "automatically generated by UIPainter ..."

    self updateContents.

    "Created: 11.9.1997 / 02:02:58 / cg"
    "Modified: 11.9.1997 / 02:03:18 / cg"
